      "type": "LinguisticObject",
      "content": "Art that treats art, its institutions, markets, archives, and viewers as the material of the work. A self-defined movement concept created by Sun & Rain Works in 2007, extending conceptual art into the system that makes art legible. Its public dossier argues credibility through genealogy, defined principles, works on view, machine-readable standards, external alignment, and provenance over time.",
